                                                    <h4 class="tta-panel-title tta-controls-icon-position-right"><a href="#a1" data-vc-accordion="" data-vc-container=".tta-container"><span class="tta-title-text"> Liver transplant surgery </span><i class="tta-controls-icon tta-controls-icon-plus"></i></a></h4>
